'''Mohammad Mohebi''' ({{langx|fa|محمد محبی}}; born 20 December 1998) is an Iranian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[winger (association football)|winger]] for Russian club [[FC Rostov|Rostov]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].<ref>{{Soccerway|mohammad-mohebi/619060}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Sepahan===
He made his debut for [[Sepahan S.C.|Sepahan]] in first fixtures of [[2019–20 Iran Pro League]] against his former team, [[Shahin Bushehr F.C.|Shahin Bushehr]], and scored first goal of match.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/match/80301 |title=بازی شاهین شهرداری بوشهر - سپاهان}}</ref>

===Santa Clara===
On 24 August 2021, Mohebi joined [[Primeira Liga]] side [[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]] on a three-year deal with [[Shahriyar Moghanlou]] moving in the opposite direction.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://cdsantaclara.com/oficial-mohebi/|title=OFICIAL: MOHEBI|publisher=[[C.D. Santa Clara]]|date=24 August 2021|access-date=25 August 2021}}</ref>

===Rostov===
On 13 July 2023, Mohebi signed with [[Russian Premier League]] club [[FC Rostov|Rostov]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Rostov|url=https://fc-rostov.ru/ru/news/2691|title=МОХАММАД МОХЕБИ – ИГРОК ФК "РОСТОВ"!|date=13 July 2023|language=ru}}</ref> He was voted league's player of the month for March 2024 after scoring 4 goals and providing 1 assist.<ref name="Mar24">{{cite web|publisher=Russian Premier League|url=https://premium.premierliga.ru/news-and-media/novosti-i-media_237.html|title=МОХАММАД МОХЕББИ – WINLINE ИГРОК МАРТА!|date=10 April 2024|language=ru}}</ref>

==International career==
He made his debut against [[Cambodia national football team|Cambodia]] in a [[2022 FIFA World Cup]] [[2022 FIFA World Cup qualification|qualification]] match on 10 October 2019, in which he scored two goals and had two assists on his debut.<ref>{{cite web |title=Iran thrash Cambodia 14-0 on marquee night for female fans |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-soccer-worldcup-iran/iran-thrash-cambodia-14-0-on-marquee-night-for-female-fans-idUSKBN1WP2O5 |website=Reuters |publisher=Reuters |access-date=10 October 2019}}</ref> He scored against [[Japan national football team|Japan]] at quarter-final of [[2023 AFC Asian Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=گل دیدنی محبی، ایران برگشت! |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1999510/%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%86%DB%8C-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A8%D8%B1%DA%AF%D8%B4%D8%AA |access-date=2024-02-04 |website=ورزش سه |language=fa}}</ref>

